msgstr "Au revoir"

#: templates/info/readme.html:117
msgid ""
"Please, enjoy OpenClinic and remember that this is <a href=\"http://"
"www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html\">free GPL software</a>."
msgstr "Veuillez profiter d'OpenClinic et n'oubliez pas qu'il s'agit d'un <a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html\">logiciel libre GPL</a>."

#: templates/info/readme.html:119
msgid ""
"OpenClinic isn't perfect, but your <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/"
"openclinic-in-django/issues\">suggestions, feedback and bug reports</a> can "
"help us to have a very well done medical records system!"
msgstr "OpenClinic n'est pas parfait, mais vos <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/openclinic-in-django/issues\">suggestions, retours et rapports de bugs</a> peuvent nous aider à avoir un excellent système de dossiers médicaux !"

